CrBoy's blog https://blog.crboy.net/posts/%E7%94%A8javascript%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%9A%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E5%99%A8%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%82%BAie/ -<p>摘自 <a href="http://leeiio.me/ie_detection_in_5_bytes/">http://leeiio.me/ie_detection_in_5_bytes/</a></p>
<pre><code>&lt;script type='text/javascript'&gt;  
var ie = !-[1,];  
alert(ie);  
&lt;/script&gt;
</code></pre>
<p>以上程式碼執行結果：IE 下返回 true，其他標準瀏覽器返回 false。<code>!-[1,]</code>，僅僅只有 6 bytes！</p>
<pre><code>&lt;script type='text/javascript'&gt;  
// Option from Dean Edwards:  
var ie = /*@cc_on!@*/false;  

// Use the commented line:  
var ie//@cc_on=1;  

// Variation (shorter variable):  
var ie = '\v'=='v';  

// Option to Gareth Hayes (former record-holder):  
var ie = !+&quot;\v1&quot;;  
&lt;/script&gt;
</code></pre>
